quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  20,25,"O maaki: \"Jooma Yanñanam ɓernde am nden"
  20,26,Newinanaa lam fiyaake am on
  20,27,Firtaa finnde nden ka ɗenngal am
  20,28,Fii yo ɓe faamu konngol am ngol
  20,29,Waɗanaa lam ballo jeyaaɗo ka ɓeynguure am
  20,30,"[Hara ko] Haaruuna musiɗɗo am on"
  20,31,Semmbinir mo darnde am
  20,32,Tawnaa mo e nder fiyaake am on
  20,33,Fii yo men Senine ko ɗuuɗi
  20,34,Men jaŋtoMaa ko ɗuuɗi
  20,35,"Pellet, An A Wonii Humpitiiɗo Men"
  20,36,"O Daali: \"Gomɗii a okkaama toraare maaɗa nden an Muusaa"
  20,37,Gomɗii Men Neeminiino ma e laawol goo
  20,38,Tuma nde Men Wahayinnoo faade e yumma maa ko Wahayinaa kon
  20,39,"[Men Daali] Bugo mo ka nder hontoore bugoɗaa nden kadi ka nder diidere, yo diidere nden kadi bugoyo mo ka fonngo; ƴetta mo gaño Am e gaño makko, Mi werlii e maaɗa Giggol immorde ka Am e fii yo a ne'e e dow ndenka Am"
  20,40,"Tuma nde banndiraawo maaɗa on yahaynoo; o wi'a: \"Enee, yo mi tinndin on e on mo no ne'a mo?\" Men artirmaa ka yumma maaɗa fii yo gite makko ɗen ɓuuɓu hara o sunaaki. Waruɗaa wonkii Men danndumaa immorde e saɗteende nden, Men jarribimaa jarrabuyeeje ñiiɓuɗaa duuɓi ka yimɓe Madyana refti aruɗaa ka fodoore ko an yo Muusaa"
  20,41,Mi Suɓimaa fii hoore-Am
  20,42,Yahu an e musiɗɗo maa on wonndude e Aayeeje Am ɗen wata on derfu e jaŋtagol Lam
  20,43,"Yahee ka Fir'awna, pellet, kanko o bewi"
  20,44,Wi'anee mo konngol newiingol bela-jo'o kanko o waajitoto maaɗum o hula
  20,45,"Ɓe maaki: \"Joomi amen, menen dey meɗen huli nde murtata e hoore amen maa nde o bewata"
  20,46,"O Daali: \"Wata on hulu, pellet, Min Miɗo wonndi e mooɗon Miɗo Nana Miɗo Yi'a"
  20,47,"Aree ka makko, wi'on: \"Menen ko Men Nulaaɓe Joomi maaɗa, accitu wonndude e amen ɓiɗɓe Israa'iila ɓen wata a leptu ɓe, gomɗii men addanii ma Aaya immorde ka Joomi maaɗa, kisiyee on wonii e on jokkuɗo Peewal ngal"
  20,48,"Gomɗii Wahayinaama e amen; wonndema, Lepte ɗen no fawii ka fennuɗo ɗuuri"
  20,49,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Ko an yo Muusaa, ko hommbo woni Joomi mooɗon"
  20,50,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Joomi amen, ko On Okkuɗo kala huunde tagu mayre ngun refti O Fewni"
  20,51,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Ko honno gire arane ɗen fewndori"
  20,52,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"ganndal ɗum no ka Joomi am e nder Deftere, Joomi am majjataa O yejjitataa"
  20,53,"On waɗanɗo on leydi ndin weƴƴitaandi, o naadani on e nder mayri laawi, O jippini immorde e kammu ngun ndiyam Men yaltiniri ɗam nooneeji immorde e puɗi sertuɗi"
  20,54,"Ñaamee aynon neemoraaɗi mo'on ɗim. Pellet, no e nder ɗum [ko jaŋtaa ɗoo] Aayeeje fii joomiraa- ɓe hakkillaaji ɗin"